title: DRAGNET (1951) 11-13 [retr?tv]
description:
DRAGNET (1951) 

11. The Big September Man    5/8/1952 
A secretary is beaten to death and the search for the killer leads police to a religious fanatic.

12. The Big Phone Call    5/22/1952 
Friday confronts a jeweler with tape recorded evidence that proves he hired someone to rob his own store.

13. The Big Casing    6/5/1952 
A man claims that his wife committed suicide right in front of him, but the evidence suggests otherwise.

Just wanted to get these from the original show up before l continue the 1967 series. :)
